                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370102-373-offence-1 t18370102-cd-55"></join>21st of December</rs>, I looking glass and frame, value 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370102-name-430" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18370102-name-430" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
